OL,4,CNike is giving its head office staff a
OL,5,Cweek's break
OL,6, Staff at Nike's corporate headquarters
OL,7, in Oregon have been given a week off to
OL,8, support their mental health, ahead of
OL,9, the return to the office in September.
OL,11,FFrom today until Friday, the US firm
OL,12,Fwill "power down" to give employees a
OL,13,Frest after a tough year.
OL,15,F"Take the time to unwind, destress and
OL,16,Fspend time with your loved ones," the
OL,17,Ffirm's head of insights Matt Marrazzo
OL,18,Fsaid in a message to staff.
OL,20,FIt follows similar moves from dating
OL,21,Fapp Bumble and Linkedin.
